init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the â€œLost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They quickly became the size of Giants.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The society that was put in place to oversee the drug, and the giants it created, failed and they were released into the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you can imagine, this was catastrophic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The giants also need to inject 9 liters of water into their veins everyday just to survive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Japanese and the Germans thought about putting the giants into a satellite which would be launched into another planet where they could grow and live peacefully.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Before the launch, there were over 100,000 giants who needed to be divided into groups of how tall they were.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people over 100 meters tall were put into one group, people who were 80 to 100 meters tall were put into another group, and the rest of

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They launched the satellite, and it reached Mars in a month.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The giants who were in group A, later called as "Super Giants" because of their immense size, grew so high that they were over 1000 meters

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They were so tall that they could easily walk on Mars without wearing oxygen masks.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Super Giants created their own cities on Mars where they could live peacefully.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: For the people in group B, they grew so tall that they could go to Earth by just floating.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people in group C could grow so tall that they could reach the stars.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They all lived happily in Mars, Earth, and the stars.
